<text><body><cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0067a" xml:id="I01.0027.0067a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0067a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 27</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0067a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>杜善勝等合邑七十人造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan><cb:div>
<pb n="0068a" xml:id="I01.0027.0068a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0068a0101" cb:type="pre">供養主佛□□　關退伽羅主杜善勝
<lb ed="I" n="0068a02"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a03"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a04"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a05"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a06"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a07"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a08"/>開明主齊承胤
<lb ed="I" n="0068a09"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a10"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a11"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a12"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a13"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a14"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a15"/>大齋主關退為亡父母亡兄
<lb ed="I" n="0068a16"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a17"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a18"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a19"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a20"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a21"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068a22"/></p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0068b" xml:id="I01.0027.0068b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0068b01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0068b0101" cb:type="pre">夫玄捴妙寂。炁末世<note n="0068001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30519"/>＝所【史】</note><note n="0068001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30519"/>【佛拓】，所【史】</note><app n="0068001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30519"/></rdg></app>能顯
<lb ed="I" n="0068b02"/>其元。真景疑槨。非季俗之<app type="star" corresp="#0068001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30519"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0068b03"/>宣其皇。是以鉢若之智難昇
<lb ed="I" n="0068b04"/>岨皆之葙。故<note n="0068002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30520"/>＝顯【史】</note><note n="0068002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30520"/>【佛拓】，顯【史】</note><app n="0068002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30520"/></rdg></app>神<g ref="#CB30521"/>歸敬慈
<lb ed="I" n="0068b05"/>萇者矣。但聖藏淟澄洪<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">臨</unclear>道
<lb ed="I" n="0068b06"/>一炁可寶塔云重菒<g ref="#CB30522"/>寶輻
<lb ed="I" n="0068b07"/>海臻。溸像寸暈則無牛号之
<lb ed="I" n="0068b08"/>潤<note n="0068003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30523"/>＝哉【史】</note><note n="0068003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30523"/>【佛拓】，哉【史】</note><app n="0068003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">哉</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30523"/></rdg></app>。山岳摧巔。海獲崩竭。偘
<lb ed="I" n="0068b09"/>神儀於清流之曲。葵永顏不
<lb ed="I" n="0068b10"/>朽者也。<note n="0068004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30524"/>＝豈【史】</note><note n="0068004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30524"/>【佛拓】，豈【史】</note><app n="0068004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">豈</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30524"/></rdg></app>緣<note n="0068005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30525"/>＝微【史】</note><note n="0068005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30525"/>【佛拓】，微【史】</note><app n="0068005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30525"/></rdg></app>工。當願正<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">備</unclear>。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b11"/>遠通慈<note n="0068006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">朖＝朗【史】</note><note n="0068006" resp="ihp" type="mod">朖【佛拓】，朗【史】</note><app n="0068006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朗</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">朖</rdg></app>。垢於<note n="0068007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𩇕＝青【史】</note><note n="0068007" resp="ihp" type="mod">𩇕【佛拓】，青【史】</note><app n="0068007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">青</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">𩇕</rdg></app>宮。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b12"/>上為皇帝　陛下。國督祚康。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b13"/>祚幾標式。合右拙塢村。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">返</unclear>願
<lb ed="I" n="0068b14"/>合邑七十人等。敬造室家石
<lb ed="I" n="0068b15"/>像一區。直鍾薩提。願合邑<note n="0068008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30526"/>＝仰【史】</note><note n="0068008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30526"/>【佛拓】，仰【史】</note><app n="0068008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">仰</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30526"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0068b16"/>隊七世。乃至<app type="star" corresp="#0068001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30519"/></rdg></app>生。朋<note n="0068009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㕛＝友【史】</note><note n="0068009" resp="ihp" type="mod">㕛【佛拓】，友【史】</note><app n="0068009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">友</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">㕛</rdg></app>眷屬。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b17"/>合霜奢梨。普洽私願。一時成
<lb ed="I" n="0068b18"/>佛。　　天寶二年保莊嚴功德飛騎尉杜思福邑子董
<lb ed="I" n="0068b19"/>建儀元年歲在毋申六月丁
<lb ed="I" n="0068b20"/>亥朔廿八日甲寅日
<lb ed="I" n="0068b21"/>願□主施□□</p></cb:div></cb:div>
